          </div>
          <div class="flex-grow">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-normal text-lexara-darkNavy mb-2">Professional</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Ideal for growing firms that need advanced features and higher volume</p>
            <div class="mb-6">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-lexara-darkNavy">$599</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600">/month</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
